Woah, V2 of my cannonball map.

This map was an pretty cool idea, and i have improved my map now.
I added my own custom textures on the map, made the ground an trigger_hurt 
and i made some changes to the ''layout'' if the map has turned 180 degrees :p

map contains:
- 18  spawnpoints
- custom textures
- pit of death :p

Want to have the textures? look on my profile!

-have fun
--hamster out

PS, should i make an tutorial ''how to make this map'' ?
